# polymer-d3pie
Polymer implementaion of d3pie

## Installation
### Bower installation 
bowere install --save polymer-d3pie

### Note:
This uses a forked version till the pull request is completed.
[d3pie](https://github.com/benkeen/d3pie) and [forked version of d3pie] (https://github.com/neolivz/d3pie)
